question: Fight Night: Who will win - Holloway or Allen? (2023-04-15)
description:
This is a market about UFC Fight Night, an upcoming mixed martial arts event produced by the Ultimate Fighting Championship that is scheduled to take place on April 15, 2023, at T-Mobile Center in Kansas City, Missouri, USA.

This is a market on whether Max Holloway or Arnold Allen will win their bout.

If Max Holloway is declared the winner of this bout, this market will resolve to “Holloway”. If Arnold Allen is declared the winner of this bout, this market will resolve to “Allen”.

If this fight is declared a draw, or if for any reason the match is not scored, postponed after April 22, 2023, 11:59:59 PM ET, or cancelled, this market will resolve 50-50.

question: Fight Night: Will Holloway win by finish? (2023-04-15)
description:
